and eats its own.

52:04.455 --> 52:07.667
"If we want to save our planet,
we have to start

52:07.875 --> 52:10.295
by changing the way we think."

52:10.503 --> 52:13.756
[laughter]

52:26.686 --> 52:28.479
Let me hit that bottle again.

52:31.482 --> 52:33.985
You think life's easy?
It's not easy.

52:34.193 --> 52:35.570
It's hard.

52:35.778 --> 52:37.864
And you got a rough deal,
I know that.

52:38.072 --> 52:39.991
Do you know what my father used
to say to me

52:40.199 --> 52:41.826
when I was growing up?

52:44.162 --> 52:46.914
Hang around with shit,
and shit gets on ya.

52:47.081 --> 52:49.751
