53:15.610 --> 53:17.612
Yes, Ms. Frankfurt.

53:21.449 --> 53:24.535
Ruthie: I had never been
in trouble before.

53:24.744 --> 53:27.372
High school was harder
than I thought.

53:27.580 --> 53:30.124
I didn't want to have to tell
my mom what happened.

53:30.333 --> 53:32.960
I didn't want to disappoint her.

53:50.478 --> 53:53.898
[Rita coughing]

53:59.862 --> 54:03.032
Mom, you need a doctor.

54:03.241 --> 54:04.617
Rita: Hmm-mm.

54:06.953 --> 54:08.746
[coughs]

54:10.289 --> 54:12.166
Sweetie, we can't afford that.

54:12.375 --> 54:16.587
I don't think
the NyQuil's working.

54:16.796 --> 54:18.131
[coughs]

54:18.339 --> 54:20.925
Ruthie: Suddenly my problems
were such smaller

54:21.134 --> 54:24.137
when I saw my mom
in so much pain.

54:24.345 --> 54:27.181
[Rita murmuring softly]

54:27.390 --> 54:29.350
You're gonna be okay, Mom.

54:29.559 --> 54:31.102
[banging on door]

54:33.855 --> 54:35.314
[banging]

54:37.066 --> 54:38.943
<i>Hey '</i>

54:39.152 --> 54:43.489
[Rita coughing, gagging]

54:43.698 --> 54:45.908
- Whoa.
- Rita: Hi.

54:46.117 --> 54:47.744
Jesus, she needs a shower, huh?

54:47.952 --> 54:49.746
Ruthie: She's too weak.

54:49.912 --> 54:52.248
