54:52.457 --> 54:54.917
I just wanted to stop by.
I got a closing.

54:55.126 --> 54:57.712
- Bye.
- Rita, coughing: Come here.

55:00.173 --> 55:01.632
[door closes]

55:08.806 --> 55:10.349
[Rita coughs]

55:16.689 --> 55:17.774
It'll be okay.

55:29.911 --> 55:31.287
[Clogs barking]

55:44.175 --> 55:45.843
Oh, Ruthie.

55:46.052 --> 55:47.386
Ms. Frankfurt.

55:49.847 --> 55:51.682
I don't know where else to go.

55:51.891 --> 55:55.102
