We need a doctor.

55:55.311 --> 55:57.188
All right, come on in, honey.
Come on!

55:57.396 --> 56:00.233
- Ruthie: Thank you.
- Frankfurt: Hurry up.

56:03.194 --> 56:04.946
Hi, Rita.

56:05.154 --> 56:07.198
What's your name?

56:07.406 --> 56:09.200
