56:10.701 --> 56:12.370
Okay.

56:12.578 --> 56:15.081
My lungs are pretty bad, too.

56:16.415 --> 56:17.667
Faster.

56:17.875 --> 56:19.043
Jacob: Yeah, I can tell.

56:19.252 --> 56:21.754
But it seems your heart
is healthy.

56:31.681 --> 56:32.765
Love you.

56:37.061 --> 56:39.730
[bell rings]

56:43.609 --> 56:45.528
Ruthie:
When I got back to school,

56:45.736 --> 56:47.822
everything had changed.

56:48.030 --> 56:50.908
[laughter, shouting]

57:02.545 --> 57:04.171
And I realized...

57:05.840 --> 57:07.341
so had I.

57:11.888 --> 57:14.932
We were already behind
on our house payments.

57:15.141 --> 57:18.728
The more time we took to pay,
the more we had to pay.

57:18.936 --> 57:21.397
Plus, business
at Tiny's had slowed.

57:23.190 --> 57:25.651
I was afraid we'd never
catch up.

57:40.666 --> 57:41.959
Mmm.

57:42.168 --> 57:43.669
I'm not drinkin' alone.

57:47.924 --> 57:49.550
Can I have some of that?

57:51.928 --> 57:53.387
Yes, you may.

57:56.432 --> 57:59.226
Say when.

57:59.435 --> 58:01.479
- Mmm, looks good.
- Yeah, okay.

58:01.687 --> 58:03.481
[both chuckle]

58:12.073 --> 58:13.407
Oh, my gosh!

58:13.616 --> 58:14.951
Long daY-

