59:21.559 --> 59:23.602
- You should go home.
- Mom, I wanna help.

59:23.811 --> 59:25.229
You got school tomorrow.
You got homework.

59:25.438 --> 59:28.190
I've already done my homework.

59:28.399 --> 59:29.817
It's late.

59:32.987 --> 59:34.071
You're drunk.

59:34.280 --> 59:35.406
What?

59:36.949 --> 59:38.409
I'm not drunk!

59:38.617 --> 59:39.744
You're drunk.

59:40.870 --> 59:42.455
[scoffs]

59:42.663 --> 59:44.707
You know how many people
have a glass of wine

59:44.915 --> 59:47.835
