in that chair over there,

01:04:55.309 --> 01:04:56.518
and, uh...

01:04:56.727 --> 01:04:59.313
I was just very lost.

01:04:59.521 --> 01:05:00.689
And, uh...

01:05:00.898 --> 01:05:03.442
you people made me feel
very welcome.

01:05:04.485 --> 01:05:05.861
[applause]

01:05:09.782 --> 01:05:12.076
Rita: Ruthie, these cookies
are really good.

01:05:14.036 --> 01:05:15.245
Ruthie?

01:05:19.625 --> 01:05:20.751
[sighs]

01:05:20.959 --> 01:05:22.461
Ruthie.

01:05:29.551 --> 01:05:31.095
