01:05:34.723 --> 01:05:36.767
How many times
can I say I'm sorry?

01:05:36.975 --> 01:05:38.352
I'm sorry.

01:05:44.024 --> 01:05:45.317
Ruthie.

01:05:48.612 --> 01:05:50.447
I'm trying to clean up.

01:05:51.990 --> 01:05:53.700
I wish you'd understand that.

01:05:55.619 --> 01:05:57.246
Ruthie.

01:06:02.167 --> 01:06:05.337
I just want things
to be good again.

01:06:05.546 --> 01:06:06.880
- Good?
- Yes.

01:06:07.089 --> 01:06:10.134
You turn everything you touch
to shit.

01:06:47.921 --> 01:06:49.423
Come here.

01:07:18.952 --> 01:07:22.873
- Can I get you some more coffee?
- Yeah, a little warm-up, thanks.

01:07:37.554 --> 01:07:42.142
Ruthie: The days felt longer
as business got slower.

01:07:42.351 --> 01:07:45.562
