and earlier.

01:07:52.653 --> 01:07:53.862
[door closes]

01:08:02.120 --> 01:08:03.622
<i>Hey '</i>

01:08:03.830 --> 01:08:05.249
<i>Hey '</i>

01:08:07.084 --> 01:08:07.918
Do you mind?

01:08:08.126 --> 01:08:09.419
