01:08:09.628 --> 01:08:11.004
Ohh!

01:08:15.842 --> 01:08:19.179
Did you know that, compared
to the size of the universe,

01:08:19.388 --> 01:08:23.183
humans are one billionth
the size of an ant?

01:08:29.273 --> 01:08:30.691
Hmm.

01:08:39.992 --> 01:08:41.451
You know when it happened to me?

01:08:46.622 --> 01:08:48.375
[whispering]
I didn't tell anybody.

01:08:48.584 --> 01:08:50.877
